<img src="//cdn.theatlantic.com/static/front//images/modules/play-button.png" style="position:absolute; left: 40px; top:30px;"/><img class="module-promo-img" src="//cdn.theatlantic.com/static/newsroom/img/2014/09/assembly_8.Still001/curation-special-report-thumb.jpg?nc4062"
    width="110" 
    height="90">
</a>
<h3 class="module-promo-hed">
    <a href="http://www.theatlantic.com/video/index/380437/crossfit-versus-yoga-choose-a-side/" data-omni-click="inherit">
        CrossFit Versus Yoga: Choose a Side    </a>
</h3>
<div class="module-promo-dek">How a workout becomes a social identity</div>
